ore" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=e9a6e33be1db9b665ce63f1c6c808c750060ba9c6235a69e8c7df2407728a9faJmltdHM9MTc3MzAxNDQwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=3cea4449-7429-6cb5-1a15-51ed75be6d5d&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9zdXBwb3J0Lm1pY3Jvc29mdC5jb20vdG9waWMvaG93LWJpbmctZGVsaXZlcnMtc2VhcmNoLXJlc3VsdHMtZDE4ZmM4MTUtYWMzNy00NzIzLWJjNjctOTIyOWNlM2ViNmEz&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP.5671,5024.1">how Bing delivers search results</a></div></div></div><div class="gs_h gs_caphead   gs_qna_fh  gs_text_truncate gs_cliptext_full gs_cliptext_tldr  "><div class="gs_temp_content gs_temp_with_iv gs_temp_with_largeqna"><div class="gs_caphead_main  "><div class="gs_text gs_mdr gsqna_renderText16"><h2 id="japanese-troops-occupied-chinas-capital-nanjing-on-december-13-1937"><span class="gs_tkn">Japanese </span><span class="gs_tkn">troops </span><span class="gs_tkn">occupied </span><span class="gs_tkn">China's </span><span class="gs_tkn">Capital </span><span class="gs_tkn">Nanjing </span><span class="gs_tkn">on </span><span class="gs_tkn">December </span><span class="gs_tkn">13, </span><span class="gs_tkn">1937</span></h2><div class="gs_p"><a class="gs_mdlink" tabindex="0" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=488c8e135613ee4541367d6dae146f8c6ab3e83855490be223bf75bd46d4d48eJmltdHM9MTc3MzAxNDQwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=3cea4449-7429-6cb5-1a15-51ed75be6d5d&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvQmF0dGxlX29mX05hbmtpbmc&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP.5671,5029.1"><span class="gs_cit_txt" data-sups="1,2,3,4" data-hover-id="1" tabindex="-1"><span class="gs_tkn">The </span><span class="gs_tkn">entry </span><span class="gs_tkn">of </span><span class="gs_tkn">Japanese </span><span class="gs_tkn">troops </span><span class="gs_tkn">into </span><span class="gs_tkn">Nanjing </span><span class="gs_tkn">on </span><span class="gs_tkn">December </span><span class="gs_tkn">13, </span><span class="gs_tkn">1937, </span><span class="gs_tkn">marked </span><span class="gs_tkn">the </span><span class="gs_tkn">beginning </span><span class="gs_tkn">of </span><span class="gs_tkn">a </span><span class="gs_tkn">horrific </span><span class="gs_tkn">period </span><span class="gs_tkn">known </span><span class="gs_tkn">as </span><span class="gs_tkn">the </span><span class="gs_tkn">Nanjing </span><span class="gs_tkn">Massacre. </span><span class="gs_tkn">The </span><span class="gs_tkn">Japanese </span><span class="gs_tkn">forces, </span><span class="gs_tkn">led </span><span class="gs_tkn">by </span><span class="gs_tkn">General </span><span class="gs_tkn">Iwane </span><span class="gs_tkn">Matsui, </span><span class="gs_tkn">had </span><span class="gs_tkn">captured </span><span class="gs_tkn">the </span><span class="gs_tkn">city </span><span class="gs_tkn">earlier </span><span class="gs_tkn">in </span><span class="gs_tkn">the </span><span class="gs_tkn">year </span><span class="gs_tkn">and, </span><span class="gs_tkn">after </span><span class="gs_tkn">a </span><span class="gs_tkn">brutal </span><span class="gs_tkn">campaign, </span><span class="gs_tkn">took </span><span class="gs_tkn">control. </span><span class="gs_tkn">The </span><span class="gs_tkn">occupation </span><span class="gs_tkn">lasted </span><span class="gs_tkn">until </span><span class="gs_tkn">March </span><span class="gs_tkn">1, </span><span class="gs_tkn">1938, </span><span class="gs_tkn">during </span><span class="gs_tkn">which </span><span class="gs_tkn">time </span><span class="gs_tkn">the </span><span class="gs_tkn">Japanese </span><span class="gs_tkn">army </span><span class="gs_tkn">committed </span><span class="gs_tkn">numerous </span><span class="gs_tkn">atrocities </span><span class="gs_tkn">against </span><span class="gs_tkn">the </span><span class="gs_tkn">local </span><span class="gs_tkn">population, </span><span class="gs_tkn">including </span><span class="gs_tkn">mass </span><span class="gs_tkn">killings, </span><span class="gs_tkn">rapes, </span><span class="gs_tkn">and </span><span class="gs_tkn">destruction </span><span class="gs_tkn">of </span><span class="gs_tkn">property. </span><span class="gs_tkn">The </span><span class="gs_tkn">Nanjing </span><span class="gs_tkn">Massacre </span><span class="gs_tkn">is </span><span class="gs_tkn">a </span><span class="gs_tkn">significant </span><span class="gs_tkn">event </span><span class="gs_tkn">in </span><span class="gs_tkn">history, </span><span class="gs_tkn">highlighting </span><span class="gs_tkn">the </span><span class="gs_tkn">scale </span><span class="gs_tkn">of </span><span class="gs_tkn">human </span><span class="gs_tkn">suffering </span><span class="gs_tkn">and </span><span class="gs_tkn">the </span><span class="gs_tkn">brutality </span><span class="gs_tkn">of </span><span class="gs_tkn">war. </span><span class="gs_tkn"></span></span></a><div class="gs_tkn gs_sup_cit gs_sup_cit1" data-priority="2" data-hover-id="1" tabindex="0"><a aria-label="View source at Wikipedia" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=488c8e135613ee4541367d6dae146f8c6ab3e83855490be223bf75bd46d4d48eJmltdHM9MTc3MzAxNDQwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=3cea4449-7429-6cb5-1a15-51ed75be6d5d&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvQmF0dGxlX29mX05hbmtpbmc&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP.5671,5029.2" tabindex="-1"><div class="gs_sm_cit" aria-label="4 citations" role="button" tabindex="-1"><div class="cico gs_sm_cit_favicon" style="width: 16px; height: 20px;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M9.49999 4H10.5C12.433 4 14 5.567 14 7.5C14 9.36856 12.5357 10.8951 10.6941 10.9948L10.5023 11L9.5023 11.0046C9.22616 11.0059 9.00127 10.783 8.99999 10.5069C8.99888 10.2614 9.17481 10.0565 9.40787 10.0131L9.4977 10.0046L10.5 10C11.8807 10 13 8.88071 13 7.5C13 6.17452 11.9685 5.08996 10.6644 5.00532L10.5 5H9.49999C9.22386 5 8.99999 4.77614 8.99999 4.5C8.99999 4.25454 9.17687 4.05039 9.41012 4.00806L9.49999 4H10.5H9.