ss="b_attribution" tabindex="-1"><cite>https://en.wikipedia.org › wiki › Battle_of_Nanking</cite></div></div></div></a></div><h2 class="" style=""><a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=c41acaebb59c13b169419d5c71436e3061265ab062ed70dd788d25ed834b1c84JmltdHM9MTc3MzAxNDQwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=3cea4449-7429-6cb5-1a15-51ed75be6d5d&amp;psq=Japanese+troops+entering+Nanjing+on+December+13%2c+1937&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvQmF0dGxlX29mX05hbmtpbmc&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5198.2" style="">Battle of Nanking - Wikipedia</a></h2><div class="b_caption"></div><div id="5476" class="b_wikiGbMod"><a class="b_wikiGbModHero" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=499ab642527591c7b50f7349fb4d170555553cb21cd114cb3fbcdae72c0212e8JmltdHM9MTc3MzAxNDQwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=3cea4449-7429-6cb5-1a15-51ed75be6d5d&amp;psq=Japanese+troops+entering+Nanjing+on+December+13%2c+1937&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvQmF0dGxlX29mX05hbmtpbmcjSGVyb1NlY3Rpb24&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5478.1">By December 13, Nanjing had fallen to the Japanese. Following the capture of the city, Japanese forces massacred Chinese prisoners of war, murdered civilians, and committed acts of looting, torture, and rape in the<strong> Nanjing Massacre</strong>.</a><div class="b_wikiGbModCards"><div><div id="b_acf_tc_1E3136C" class="b_acf_card b_wikiGbModCard acf_t_c acf_padding b_acf_bckgnd" link=""><a title="" class="b_acf_card_link" target="_blank" tabindex="0" aria-label="Overview" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=5dc4611f6809b940020351e7e0b0d90dffa0935dcdca296582d97495b25013d6JmltdHM9MTc3MzAxNDQwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=3cea4449-7429-6cb5-1a15-51ed75be6d5d&amp;psq=Japanese+troops+entering+Nanjing+on+December+13%2c+1937&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvQmF0dGxlX29mX05hbmtpbmcjT3ZlcnZpZXc&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5480.1"></a><div class="acf_t_c_content "><div class="acf_t_c_inner"><div class="acf_t_c_title_cont"><div style="-webkit-line-clamp: 1; line-clamp: 1;" class="acf_t_c_title" role="heading" aria-level="2">Overview</div><div class="acf_t_c_chevron_container"><div class="acf_t_c_chevron_icon"><svg id="acfchevronicon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M6.40617 3.20041C6.10264 3.48226 6.08506 3.95681 6.36691 4.26034L9.89303 8L6.36691 11.7397C6.08506 12.0432 6.10264 12.5177 6.40617 12.7996C6.7097 13.0815 7.18425 13.0639 7.4661 12.7603L11.4661 8.51034C11.7333 8.22258 11.7333 7.77743 11.4661 7.48966L7.4661 3.23966C7.18425 2.93613 6.7097 2.91856 6.40617 3.20041Z"></path></svg></div></div></div><p style="-webkit-line-clamp: 6; line-clamp: 6; overflow:hidden;" class="acf_t_c_body">The Battle of Nanking (or Nanjing) was fought in early December 1937 during the Second Sino-Japanese War between the Chinese National Revolutionary Army and the Imperial Japanese Army for control of Nanjing (Chinese: 南京; pinyin: Nánjīng), …</p></div></div></div></div><div class="b_wikiGbModImageCard"><div class="b_bimgSetrcw"><div class="bimgclgsw19113"><div class="cico b_bwrich_icma" style="width:310px;height:198px;"><a title="View details" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;q=imgurl:https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Attacking_the_Gate_of_China02.jpg/330px-Attacking_the_Gate_of_China02.jpg&amp;iss=sbi&amp;mode=overlay&amp;idpbck=1&amp;idpp=WikiGoBig&amp;FORM=IDPWGB&amp;thid=ODL.d1ee7b1321deadbc7eb00863d6ff4ce0&amp;mediaurl=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Attacking_the_Gate_of_China02.jpg/330px-Attacking_the_Gate_of_China02.jpg" h="ID=SERP,5479.1" data-idpignore="1" class=""><img height="198" width="310" data-src-hq="https://th.bing.com/th/id/ODL.d1ee7b1321deadbc7eb00863d6ff4ce0?w=310&amp;h=198&amp;c=7&amp;rs=1&amp;bgcl=ffff14&amp;r=0&amp;o=6&amp;pid=AlgoBlockDebug" role="presentation" data-priority="2" id="emb67DA511F" class="rms_img" src="./Japanese troops entering Nanjing on December 13, 1937 - Search_files/ODL.d1ee7b1321deadbc7eb00863d6ff4ce0" loading="lazy" data-bm="41"></a></div></div></div></div><div class="b_wikiGbModImageCard"><div class="cico b_bwrich_icma" style="width:310px;height:200px;"><a title="View details" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;q=imgurl:https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c1/Iwane_Matsui.jpg/250px-Iwane_Matsui.jpg&amp;iss=sbi&amp;mode=overlay&amp;idpbck=1&amp;idpp=WikiGoBig&amp;FORM=IDPWGB&amp;thid=ODL.ceeac72b6e11f0de9c6a11f9cc70490d&amp;mediaurl=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c1/Iwane_Matsui.jpg/250px-Iwane_Matsui.jpg" h="ID=SERP,5482.1" data-idpignore="1"><img height="200" width="310" data-src-hq="https://th.bing.com/th/id/ODL.ceeac72b6e11f0de9c6a11f9cc70490d?w=310&amp;h=200&amp;c=7&amp;rs=1&amp;bgcl=fffffd&amp;r=0&amp;o=6&amp;pid=AlgoBlockDebug" role="presentation" data-priority="2" id="emb14FA9CBBD" class="rms_img" src="./Japanese troops entering Nanjing on December 13, 1937 - Search_files/ODL.ceeac72b6e11f0de9c6a11f9cc70490d" loading="lazy" data-bm="42"></a></div></div><div><div id="b_acf_tc_2E3213C" class="b_acf_card b_wikiGbModCard acf_t_c acf_padding b_acf_bckgnd" link=""><a title="" class="b_acf_card_link" target="_blank" tabindex="0" aria-label="Background" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=e511a4562e8f543273f47dff580050a21a59dbec9f927da2079758fe20f17f19JmltdHM9MTc3MzAxNDQwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=3cea4449-7429-6cb5-1a15-51ed75be6d5d&amp;psq=Japanese+troops+entering+Nanjing+on+December+13%2c+1937&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvQmF0dGxlX29mX05hbmtpbmcjQmFja2dyb3VuZA&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5481.1"></a><div class="acf_t_c_content "><div class="acf_t_c_inner"><div class="acf_t_c_title_cont"><div style="-webkit-line-clamp: 1; line-clamp: 1;" class="acf_t_c_title" role="heading" aria-level="2">Background</div><div c