lt</span></div></div></div></a></div><h2 class=""><a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=b4684b1f00f144749058b53426ba874cd0a76f511d6102d8030acc2e3be59b7cJmltdHM9MTc3MzAxNDQwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=3cea4449-7429-6cb5-1a15-51ed75be6d5d&amp;psq=Japanese+troops+entering+Nanjing+on+December+13%2c+1937&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudW5lc2NvaWNkaC5vcmcvZW5nL3N1Yi5waHA_bWVudWtleT0yODkmbW9kPXZpZXcmbm89MjQ1NjgmbGlzdENudD0xMCZjb2RlMT0wMDAwMDAwMyZjb2RlMj0wMDAwMDAyNA&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5327.2">ICDH &gt; Memory of the World &gt; MoW International Registers</a></h2><div class="b_caption"><p class="b_lineclamp2">On December 13, 1937, after capturing Nanjing, the capital of China at that time, Japanese troops launched a massacre against Nanjing residents and disarmed Chinese soldiers which lasted as long …</p></div></li><li class="b_algo" data-id="" iid="SERP.5742" data-bm="16"><div class="b_tpcn"><a class="tilk" aria-label="historysnacks.io" redirecturl="" tabindex="-1" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=0f1b3fa89032184ccb383c435d394d7423ae81bd32dc000487252dbd8237ec2fJmltdHM9MTc3MzAxNDQwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=3cea4449-7429-6cb5-1a15-51ed75be6d5d&amp;psq=Japanese+troops+entering+Nanjing+on+December+13%2c+1937&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9oaXN0b3J5c25hY2tzLmlvL2V2ZW50L2EweTVqZmI0Lw&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5345.1"><div class="tpic"><div class="wr_fav" data-priority="2"><div class="cico siteicon" style="width:32px;height:32px;"><img src="./Japanese troops entering Nanjing on December 13, 1937 - Search_files/ODF.L9xkw7KqtpxJKUM2W3XwgA" height="32" width="32" alt="Global web icon" class="rms_img" data-bm="76"></div></div></div><div class="tptxt"><div class="tptt">historysnacks.io</div><div class="tpmeta"><div class="b_attribution" tabindex="-1"><cite>https://historysnacks.io › event</cite></div></div></div></a></div><h2 class=""><a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=0f1b3fa89032184ccb383c